metadata.description:
Only bound by blood, the rest are just wound.

what are you going to do if you have many siblings but don't feel protected and feel like stranger or even like an enemy?

i would say my whole life is about to seek the one i can feel safe enough to be around. but i can't find it on all my brothers and sisters since my childhood.

yeah, it's all about me and my entire life story. it's start with when the safest place called home is no longer safe :)
